modules.description: Provides functions to transform OCaml patterns by distributing guards over or-patterns, resolving warning 57. Operates on pattern expressions and guard conditions within the abstract syntax tree. Used to simplify complex pattern matching scenarios involving multiple guarded alternatives.

Provides functions to transform pattern matching cases into expanded forms and to process expressions within a ppx extension context. Works with OCaml AST cases, expressions, and extension rules. Used to rewrite guarded patterns into explicit case structures during macro expansion.
